Package gwendolyncrclclient

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CRCLClient
    CRCL client written in java.
    CShape
    Shape describes the basic attributes of the world model ojects Each object has a name, type and location.
    CShape.inference_type
    inference structure for describing a shape inferences.
    CShapes
    Shapes is a container for the shapes in the kitting scene, the definitions defining the parts in the scene (gears, kits, supply vessel, as well as the slots in a tray).
    Globals
    Globals is a wrapper for global flags and other general purpose utilities.
    GwendolynCrclClient
    GwendolynCrclClient is the main class.
    KittingDemo
    Provides methods to perform or fake performing the kitting demonstration for the fanuc robot.
    rcs_robot
    Basic definitions of the robot that will be manipulated.
    rcs_world
    model information about the objects in the scene.
    StatusThread
    Runs a separate thread to retrieve and report on the status of crcl communication.
    TestCases
    A smattering of methods to test the crcl communication as well as lower level simulation validaity.
